Modifications
-------------
This backport adapts RCLootCouncil to run on World of Warcraft 3.3.5a
(Wrath of the Lich King) / TrinityCore. Changes include:

  * Backporting modern WoW APIs to the 3.3.5a client
  * Replacing unsupported game functions
  * Wrath of the Lich King compatibility fixes
  * TrinityCore 3.3.5a support

Backport modifications by Jedborg, 2024-2026.
See changelog.md for the detailed history of changes.

